messages.messageBody:
Sharon,

I would love to get together. The zoo is a great idea. We just got a membership to go all we can stand. If you would prefer we could get together somewhere else. If you would like to email me directly at kinkade@... we can work out details.

Rebecca
----- Original Message -----
From: Sharon Rudd
To: AlwaysLearning@yahoogroups.com
Sent: Tuesday, April 30, 2002 11:28 AM
Subject: Re: [AlwaysLearning] Where is everyone located?


Rebecca
I am about 30 miles north of you, in Nassau county.
Come on over....we are home a lot. Or we could go to
the zoo or something. Or you could come camp out to
the PARTY IN THE WOODS. May 1 - 15. There are three
families coming, at different times. Some overlap
would make it even more fun.

I look forward to hearing from you.
Sharon of the Swamp

I was wondering where everyone is located? Do any of you ever get
together? We are in Jacksonville. We haven't been able to find a
